dc_description_s: These line and point data layers represent trails and trail intersections for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2016. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Lincoln_Trails_2016.gdb. Included here are features: IceAgeTrail, SnowATVIntersection, SnowmobileTrails, SummerATV.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
